# Learning Management System (LMS)

## Description

This Learning Management System (LMS) allows students to enroll in courses, interact with tutors, and track their learning progress. Tutors can manage their courses, view earnings, and communicate with students.

Key features include:

- Course enrollment and management
- Tutor-student messaging
- Payment integration (Paystack, etc.)
- User-friendly dashboards for tutors and students

## Technologies Used

- **Backend**: Node.js, Express.js
- **Database**: MongoDB
- **Payment Gateway**: Paystack
- **Authentication**: JWT
- **Other Tools**: Mongoose, Dotenv
